node_6.subject: Klaus Mueller
node_6.description: This is Klaus Mueller's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, head to the library at Oak Hill College at 8:00 am, spend the morning and afternoon conducting research and writing his paper, take a lunch break at 12:00 pm at Hobbs Cafe, continue with his research and writing until 5:00 pm, have dinner at 5:00 pm, spend the evening relaxing and reading for leisure.
